and said visitors come back committed to saving the rain forests 
he said tours show tourists its destruction firsthand 
i can show you scores of letters from people who have taken my 
voyages who have become involved right away with the earth 
brill said you should see the letters to the governments to 
protect the jungles and to protect the indians 
