xu spoke friday in bangkok his comments were reported by the 
official chinese news agency xinhua 
he was quoted as saying the two countries remain divided over 
two key points the status of cambodias government during the 
transition period before a new administration and the status of 
its army during that period 
china is the principal backer of three cambodian guerrilla 
factions including the khmer rouge fighting the 
vietnameseinstalled government in phnom penh 
there have been proposals that the united nations become 
involved in adminstering the country to prepare the way for 
