the miner scrambled on all fours 
through mud along shaft no 6 in the red star mine cursing as he 
knocked loose a support 
his helmet lamp bobbed in the gloom as he jammed the metal jack 
back under roughcut ceiling beams in the low tunnel in the heart 
of the donetsk basin the largest soviet coal field 
the miners more than a quartermile beneath makeyevka were 
