correspondent who had crawled 500 feet along a low tunnel to talk 
with them and see their working conditions 
this is how we work said a miner named alexander lying on 
his side using a broadbladed shovel to ladle lumps of hard coal 
onto a conveyer belt driven by chains that roared a few inches 
from his nose 
a coworker named sergei lifted a drill and long bit to show how 
