obeid said he believed the colleges 233 students just want to 
study 
they are very eager to continue their education he said 
the other palestinian universities that remain closed are 
bethlehem university islamic university hebron university 
annajah university and bir zeit university 
during the shutdown instruction has continued in the makeshift 
underground classes but attendance was sporadic and the 
education far below the normal standards 
