expectancy rate was increasing to about 70 years 
since then the rate had fallen in some areas of worst 
pollution he said that in some heavily polluted areas like 
northern bohemia the life expectancy is 10 years below the western 
european average 
the ministers said one of the leading causes of pollution in 
