a few disappearances are to be expected considering the stress 
factor these days but this vanishing act involves 30000 a month 
its been going on since last october and that means the total now 
is well over 200000 
those are significant numbers nothing like it has been seen 
before and making it more mysterious is the absence of clues 
these men havent been laid off for example because they havent 
