used to finance one of his atlantic city resorts the most visible 
signal yet of the trouble dogging his real estate empire but 
another prominent personality with the initials dt basked in more 
positive publicity luring hordes of moviegoers as the hollywood 
blockbuster dick tracy opened around the country 
